response.overview: New Orleans is the party city, the musical mecca bursting with feel-good rhythms that run deep in your veins, but there's one infectious beat, one party that's been rocking the city for 25 years, and it's called Bounce.  You ALready Know is the story of Bounce music, diving into its rich history from the late 80s until now. A soul-stirring New Orleanian narrative, told through the eyes of youth worker and King of Bounce, DJ Jubilee.
response.tagline: A New Orleans Movie to feed your soul, free your mind and shake dat booty.
response.title: You Already Know
